children.text: Grab a bar stool or sit near the fireplace and sample local wines, spirits, and beers as you unwind from a full day of charging hard.

data.title: Monte Wolfes
data.subtitle: Monte Wolfes is your all-day quick stop

children.text: Did you lose your granola bar sending it off the Wall? No worries, Monte Wolfes is your all-day quick stop. Serving breakfast burritos, tacos, and grab n go snacks, Montes is your go-to for fast and easy gruboh, and dont forget about the full bar!
Dive into a hot tasty pizza after a long day of ripping the mountain. The Cornice welcomes casual vibes and hungry stomachs.
Your mountain one-stop shop. Whether youre looking for kitchen staples, a full-service deli, snacks, or a vast selection of craft beer, the G-Store has you covered.
